To get this project for your pc you need.

Open Empty folder
Open terminal inside it 

* note * 
apache2 should be stoped 
-> sudo service apache2 stop 
And make sure to have .env file 


Than do the following commands 

-> git init
-> git pull https://github.com/YaroslavTheSlav/The_News_Week_Website.git

then 
-> composer instal

and to start the project use the following command 
-> make 

to stop the project do 
-> make stop 